SIMPLE: funding
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Funding
<hw>Fund"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Providing a fund for
the payment of the interest or principal of a debt.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Investing in the public funds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Funding system</b></col>, <cd>a system or scheme of
finance or revenue by which provision is made for paying the interest or
principal of a public debt.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fundless</ent>⟦br⟧
